data.text:
A biography of Thomas Joseph O’Connell (1882-1969) by Dr. Antonia McManus.

TD (1922-32)

Labour Party Leader (1927-32)

General Secretary of the Irish National Teachers’ Organisation (1916-48)

Senator (1938-44, 48-51 and 54-57)

‘The best Minister for Education Ireland never had’
